From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Namecoin Integration <namecoin@example.org>
Date: Wed, 16 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 0010] Address bar security indicators for .bit domains

Add Namecoin-specific security indicators to the address bar (URL bar)
for .bit domains. Three states:
  - nmc-secure  (teal/green): DANE-TLSA validated certificate
  - nmc-warning (yellow/amber): HTTP-only or no TLSA record
  - nmc-error   (red): TLSA validation failed

Modifies UrlbarInput.sys.mjs to detect .bit security state and applies
CSS classes to the identity icon. Follows existing Proton design patterns
for EV/DV certificate indicators.

Bug: XXXXXX — [namecoin] Phase 3: Address bar security indicators
---
